item.title: Trauma.....A Therapy Theory.
item.description: Trauma....something so common but also so taboo. We’ve all been throw things in life that have in some way shaped who we are. I’m just talking about a little bit of the things I’ve seen and been through growing up in hopes that talking about it can help me get a better understanding of how it effected me and also how it’s contributed to the person I am today. Hope you all enjoy and let me know how ya have dealt with your own personal life happenings --- This episode is sponsored by · Anchor: The easiest way to make a podcast. https://anchor.fm/app
